\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Vi\'e4ll\'e1\'e1-uv mad\'e2r\'e1kku see\u331\'3fg\'e2st?
\par \endash  Mad\'e2r\'e1kku vi\'e4ll\'e1\'e1 kistoost. Kisto lii kale v\'e1h\'e1 tego se\u331\'3fg\'e2.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Lii-uv \'e1\'e1hust talle ijj\'e2p\'e4i\'f0i pajalist? sun koij\'e2dij oppeet.
\par \endash  \'c1\'e1hust lii vielgis piivt\'e2s pajalist. Tot lii eresl\'e1g\'e1n piivt\'e2s ko ijj\'e2p\'e4i\'f0i.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Lii-uv \'e1\'e1hu ijj\'e2piht\'e2sist-uv}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524  kuob\'9e\'e2 kove tego muu ijj\'e2p\'e4\'e4i\'f0ist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Ij lah. Tast ij lah kove. Tot lii tu\'9ae vielgis piivt\'e2s.
\par \endash  Ij-uvks \'e1kku innig ku\'e1ssin kocc\'e1\'e1?
\par \endash  Na ij.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Pu\'e1ht\'e1-uv talle sier\'e2di\'f0gin, ko u\'e1\'f0\'e1?
\par \endash  Ij pyevti. Talle tu\'9a u\'e1\'f0\'e1.
\par \endash  Talle mad\'e2r\'e1kku ij pyevti lih\'e2tti\'f0 juolgijdis ige kie\'f0\'e2idis ige suorm\'e2idiskin. Mun kale pu\'e1vt\'e1m. Enni, mun jiem lah j\'e1\'e1mm\'e1m. Keej\'e2!
\par Si\'e4mm\'e1st oinim, maht nieid\'e2\'9a hi\'e4ilutt\'e2l\'e2i kie\'f0\'e2idis j\'e1 juolgijdis j\'e1 suorm\'e2idis j\'e1 ke\'e8\'e8\'e2lij tuo\'f0\'e2\'9ati\'f0 munjin, et l\'e2i vala elimin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Na ij pyevtigin, v\'e4stidim.
\par Jurdim, et}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524  lijjim u\'e1li pyereest \'e8ielgim, maggaar tiileest suu mad\'e2r\'e1kku t\'e4\'e4l l\'e2i, mut ko\'e8\'e8\'e2mu\'9a\'e2
in ij pu\'e1tt\'e1m lopp\'e2.
\par \endash  Na lii-uv tot mad\'e2r\'e1kku panijdis pooss\'e2m ovdilgo sun u\'e1\'f0\'f0\'e1i kiiston?
\par \endash  Na tast kale jiem tie\'f0e. Viss\'e2h\'e2n.
\par \endash  L\'e2i-uv \'e1\'e1hust-uv apinap\'e4ninjuo\'f0\'e2s tego m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 ust?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Na jiem tie\'f0e maggaar p\'e4ninjuo\'f0\'e2s. \'c1\'e1hust i\'e4 lama\'9a jieij\'e2s p\'e4\'e4nih.
\par \endash  Mun i\'e4l\'e1m ain pos\'e2\'f0\'e2tmin ovdilgo u\'e1\'f0\'f0\'e1\'e1m. Lii-uv mad\'e2r\'e1kku-uv pos\'e2\'f0\'e2tt\'e2m?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Na viss\'e2h\'e2n.
\par \endash  Maggaar loovd\'e2 \'e1\'e1hust lii? L\'e1\'e1-uv \'e1\'e1hu kistoost lakanah? Muu see\u331\'3fg\'e2st l\'e1\'e1 t\'e4\'e4l fiskis lakanah. Suu sav\'e2st\'e2ll\'e2m kullui jotkuumin veik mon kuhh\'e1\'e1.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Maht jis tu\'e1lvu\'e8\'e8im suu ke\'e8\'e8\'e2\'f0 mad\'e2r\'e1\'e1hu? ettim k\'e1ll\'e1s\'e2n.
\par Sun kej\'e2stij muu j\'e1 ee\'f0\'e2i:
\par \endash  Na jis jurd\'e1h, et tast lii i\'9ae, te tu\'e1lvu peri! sun ee\'f0\'e2i. Mut mun kale jiem vyelgi!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Na mondiet jieh? koij\'e2dim.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Munjin lii p\'e1\'e1cc\'e1m ti\'e4tul\'e1g\'e1n kove, maggaar tuu \'e1kku l\'e2i, j\'e1 tom \'e1\'e1igum si\'e4ilutti\'f0
, sun v\'e4stidij.
\par \endash  Muoi manneen forg\'e2 ke\'e8\'e8\'e2\'f0 mad\'e2r\'e1\'e1hu, ettim nieid\'e2s\'e2n. Tun u\'e1\'9euh orroo\'f0 eeni askeest. \'c1kku vi\'e4ll\'e1\'e1 kistoost j\'e1 sust lii vielgis piivt\'e2s pajalist. Sust l\'e1\'e1 \'e8almeh kidd\'e2. Mad\'e2r
\'e1kku ij liih\'e2d innig ige s\'e1\'e1rnu maiden mut tu\'9ae u\'e1\'f0\'e1. Tast ij taarb\'e2\'9a pooll\'e2\'f0.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 
\par Ko kuhes }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid5466320\charrsid1844524 auto}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 m\'e4
tki nuuv\'e2i, \'9aood\'e2i mest\'e2 jo hu\'e1ppu. Ulmuuh \'e8okk\'e1jii jo sivnedemkappelist j\'e1 l\'e2im aaib\'e2s majemuuh, ki\'e4h tohon pottii. Muoi moon\'e1im vala ke\'e8\'e8\'e2\'f0 \'e1\'e1hu. Ko moon\'e2im tohon siis\'e2, te vistig ooinijm tu
\'9ae kisto jyelgikeeji j\'e1 koolg\'e2i moonn\'e2\'f0 aaib\'e2s kisto paald\'e2n, et ooinij vala mu\'e1\'f0uid-uv. \'c1kku l\'e2i vaib\'e2m, nuuh\'e2m. Sun kale tarb\'e2\'9aij vuoi\u331\'3f\'e2st\'e2s\'e2s.
\par \endash  Ij taarb\'e2\'9a pooll\'e2\'f0, nieid\'e2\'9a ee\'f0\'e2i munjin ko keej\'e2i j\'e1\'e1}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 mm\'e1m mad\'e2r\'e1\'e1hus muu askeest.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 Mudoi sun oroi aaib\'e2s josk\'e2 \endash  tego li\'e8ij finnim v\'e1st\'e1d\'e2s puoh ko\'e8\'e8\'e2mu\'9a\'9a\'e1id.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 Kuosk\'e2ttim \'e1\'e1hu nier\'e2. Tot l\'e2i koolm\'e2s j\'e1 toos ij lama\'9a suot\'e2s kuosk\'e2\'f0. Rottejim kiett\'e2n medd\'e2
l. Tot ij lama\'9a oll\'e1gin taggaar suot\'e2s, liegg\'e2 tobdo ko }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 kuosk\'e2t nube ulmuu.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 Must l\'e2i taggaar tobdo, et nieid\'e2\'9a v\'e1h\'e1 ibbeerd\'9akuo\'f0ij, mii j\'e4\'e4mmim jie\'9aalnees l\'e2i. Ko l\'e2im valm\'e2
\'9aeh, te h\'e4vdidemtoim\'e2ttuv almai koij\'e2dij must, et u\'e1\'9e\'9eu-uv lohe pieij\'e2\'f0 kidd\'e2. Ko lopedim, te sun vistig piej\'e2i liijne \'e1\'e1hu mu\'e1\'f0ui ool\'e2 j\'e1}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524  piej\'e2i lohe kidd\'e2. Nuuvt l\'e2im u\'e1in\'e1m \'e1\'e1hu majemuu keerdi.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Kuus mad\'e2r\'e1kku t\'e4\'e4lgis \'9aood\'e2i, koij\'e2dij nieid\'e2\'9a ko \'e8ok\'e1nijm sivnedemkappel\'e2
n eres ulmui koosk\'e2n.
\par \endash  Na tot vi\'e4ll\'e1\'e1 vala-uv tuon kistoost, \'e8aittim. Mu\'9at\'e1h-uv ko \'e8eeci piej\'e2i kisto kidd\'e2 j\'e1 \'e1kku pa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 
asij tohon?
\par \endash  Joo, kullui culijdem muu pi\'e4lj\'e1n.
\par 
\par Munjin u\'e1pis papp\'e2 s\'e1\'e1rnui. Sun ti\'e4duttij tom, et \'e1kku l\'e2i s\'e4mmil\'e2\'9a j\'e1 tom, et ij tubd\'e2m taan ulmuu eellim S\'e4\'e4mist. Tot l\'e2i kuitt\'e2g tot piir\'e2s, kost sun majemuid aigijdis eelij, veik l\'e2i-uv kartt\'e2
m S\'e4\'e4mist k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 uh\'e1s. Tot l\'e2i meiddei tot piir\'e2s, mast jie\'9a \'e1\'e1hu miel\'e2st\'e2n mu\'9at\'e1m: jieij\'e2
s tuuveest keessiv j\'e1 t\'e4lviv u\'f0\'f0\'e2 tuuveest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 Viijm\'e2g sivnedemtil\'e1l\'e2\'9avuot\'e2 nuuv\'e2i, j\'e1 ulmuuh vuolgii sat\'e2\'e8\'e8i\'f0 kisto h\'e4vdien\'e2m\'e2n.
\par \endash  Kuus mij t\'e4\'e4lgis vyelgip? kullui oppeet ko\'e8\'e8\'e2mu\'9a muu }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 paald\'e2st.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Mij vyelgip tu\'e1lvu\'f0 \'e1\'e1hu h\'e4vdien\'e2m\'e2n.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Mii tot h\'e4vdieenn\'e2mgis lii?
\par \endash  Tot lii t\'e1\'e1gu aaib\'e2s alda. \'c1\'e1hu kisto pi\'e4ijoo forg\'e2 tohon. Mij moonn\'e2p tohon v\'e4\'e4zin. Tun u\'e1in\'e1h aaib\'e2s forg\'e2, mii tobbeen t\'e1b\'e1htuv\'e1.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 U\'e1nihis v\'e4zzimm\'e4\'e4\'f0hi ma\u331\'3fa sat\'e2\'e8\'e8emju\'e1vkk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 u juovd\'e2i kistoin h\'e4\'e4vdi kuuvl.
\par \endash  Keej\'e2 enni, ko toh pieijih kisto tuon stuorr\'e2 roog\'e1n!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Mun ti\'e4\'f0\'e1m. Tot lii kie\u331\'3f\'e2lis rogge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Lii-uv mad\'e2r\'e1kku vala-uv tuon kistoost?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  Lii. Taam ko\'e8odeh h\'e4vdidm\'e2n, ko j\'e1\'e1mm\'e1m ulmuu ruum\'e2\'9a pi\'e4ijoo kistoost en\'e2m\'e2n.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 \endash  P\'e1\'e1c\'e1-uv \'e1kku tohon roog\'e1n?
\par \endash  Kale p\'e1\'e1c\'e1, v\'e4stidim.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af319 \ltrch\fcs0 \f319\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang9275\langfe1035\langnp9275\insrsid10634677\charrsid1844524 Jurduin\'e2n juuttim suul\'e2n kulm\'e2lov ihheed majaskulij, ko jie\'e8\'e8\'e2n ee\'e8i j\'e1 \'e4ijih jaamijn. Munjin mu\'9at\'e2
lui talle, et ee\'e8i j\'e1 \'e4ijih l\'e1in moonn\'e2m aalman.
